<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Zuhura Wangara — PR & Marketing Consultant</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0f1f3d;
    --navy-mid: #1a3260;
    --navy-light: #2a4a8a;
    --white: #f5f5f0;
    --grey-mid: #b0b0a8;
    --grey-dark: #555550;
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --accent: #c8a96e;
    --accent-light: #e8d4a8;
  }
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--black); color: var(--white); overflow-x: hidden; cursor: none; }

  /* CURSOR */
  .cursor { width: 12px; height: 12px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 50%; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999; transition: transform 0.15s ease; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); }
  .cursor-ring { width: 36px; height: 36px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.5); border-radius: 50%; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 9998; transition: transform 0.08s ease, opacity 0.2s; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); }

  /* BG GRID */
  body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(200,169,110,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200,169,110,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px; pointer-events: none; }

  /* NAV */
  nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; padding: 1.4rem 4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: rgba(10,10,10,0.88); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); }
  .nav-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.2rem; list-style: none; }
  .nav-links a { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-mid); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; cursor: none; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

  /* HERO */
  #hero { min-height: 100vh; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; padding: 8rem 4rem 6rem 6rem; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .hero-tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; }
  .hero-tag::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 2rem; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(3rem, 5.5vw, 5.2rem); line-height: 1.0; color: var(--white); }
  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); display: block; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 480px; margin: 1.8rem 0 2.8rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .hero-sub strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }
  .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.85rem 2rem; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.25s; cursor: none; }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); font-weight: 500; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline { border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.4); color: var(--accent); }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(200,169,110,0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .hero-right { position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-graphic { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, rgba(42,74,138,0.35) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 80%, rgba(200,169,110,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%); }
  .hero-stat-grid { position: relative; z-index: 2; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2); }
  .hero-stat { background: rgba(10,10,10,0.9); padding: 2.2rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .hero-stat-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .hero-stat-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-mid); }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .section-wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 3rem; }
  .section-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 1.5rem; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  h2 em { color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; }
  .divider { height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,169,110,0.3), transparent); }

  /* ABOUT */
  #about { background: var(--black); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .about-text p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85; color: var(--grey-mid); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .about-text p strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }
  .about-text p em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .about-facts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; }
  .fact-item { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1); padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1.1rem; align-items: flex-start; transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
  .fact-item:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.05); border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.25); }
  .fact-icon { font-size: 1.2rem; min-width: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
  .fact-title { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .fact-desc { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* WINS / PORTFOLIO */
  #wins { background: rgba(15,31,61,0.4); }
  .wins-intro { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--grey-mid); max-width: 620px; margin-bottom: 3rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
  .portfolio-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.15); margin-bottom: 1.5px; }
  .win-card { background: var(--black); padding: 2rem 1.8rem; transition: background 0.25s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .win-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--accent); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .win-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .win-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
  .win-outlet { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .win-role { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-dark); margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
  .win-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 0.22rem 0.55rem; border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2); color: var(--grey-dark); text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: 1px; }
  .tag-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

  .outlets-bar { background: rgba(10,10,10,0.95); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); border-top: none; padding: 1.6rem 2rem; }
  .outlets-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(200,169,110,0.4); margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center; }
  .outlets-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.8rem 2.5rem; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
  .outlet-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--grey-dark); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .outlet-name:hover { color: var(--grey-mid); }

  .metrics-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); margin-top: 1.5px; }
  .metric { background: var(--black); padding: 2rem 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
  .metric-num { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--white); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .metric-num span { color: var(--accent); }
  .metric-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-dark); }

  /* SERVICES */
  #services { background: var(--black); }
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); }
  .service-card { background: var(--black); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; transition: background 0.25s; }
  .service-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
  .service-num { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: rgba(200,169,110,0.35); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .service-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.3; }
  .service-desc { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .service-price { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  /* IDEAL CLIENTS */
  #clients { background: rgba(15,31,61,0.25); }
  .clients-intro { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--grey-mid); max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 3rem; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; }
  .clients-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .client-card { background: var(--black); padding: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: flex-start; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .client-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
  .client-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; min-width: 2rem; }
  .client-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .client-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; }
  .not-fit { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-radius: 2px; }
  .not-fit-title { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-dark); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .not-fit p { font-size: 0.87rem; color: var(--grey-dark); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  #testimonials { background: var(--black); }
  .testi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); margin-bottom: 1.5px; }
  .testi-grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5px; background: rgba(200,169,110,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.12); border-top: none; }
  .testi-card { background: var(--black); padding: 2.2rem 2rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .testi-card:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.03); }
  .testi-quote { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3rem; color: rgba(200,169,110,0.2); line-height: 0.5; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .testi-text { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.75; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .testi-author { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); }
  .testi-role { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--grey-dark); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
  .testi-placeholder { background: var(--black); border: none; padding: 2.2rem 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center; min-height: 200px; }
  .testi-placeholder p { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(200,169,110,0.25); text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1.8; }

  /* CONTACT */
  #contact { background: rgba(15,31,61,0.3); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-left p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--grey-mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .contact-left p strong { color: var(--white); }
  .contact-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .contact-link { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1); padding: 1.1rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; cursor: none; }
  .contact-link:hover { background: rgba(200,169,110,0.06); border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.3); }
  .contact-link-icon { font-size: 1rem; }
  .contact-link-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-dark); flex: 1; }
  .contact-link-value { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--grey-mid); }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; }
  .form-field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .form-field label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--grey-dark); padding: 0.6rem 0 0; }
  .form-field input, .form-field textarea, .form-field select { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.15); border-top: none; color: var(--white); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.9rem 1rem; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; appearance: none; }
  .form-field input:focus, .form-field textarea:focus, .form-field select:focus { border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.5); background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04); }
  .form-field textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 110px; }
  .form-field select option { background: #1a1a1a; }
  .form-submit { margin-top: 0.5rem; background: var(--accent); color: var(--black); border: none; padding: 1rem 2rem; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 500; cursor: none; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--accent-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .form-note { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.58rem; color: var(--grey-dark); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-top: 0.8rem; text-align: center; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { background: var(--black); border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1); padding: 2rem 6rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
  .footer-name { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); }
  .footer-copy { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--grey-dark); }

  /* ANIMATIONS */
  .fade-in { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease; }
  .fade-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.2rem; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.6rem; }
    #hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-left { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .hero-right { display: none; }
    .section-wrap { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-grid, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .portfolio-grid, .services-grid, .testi-grid, .testi-grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .clients-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .metrics-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; }
    body { cursor: auto; }
    .cursor, .cursor-ring { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">ZW</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#wins">Portfolio</a></li>
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#clients">Ideal Clients</a></li>
    <li><a href="#testimonials">Kind Words</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Work With Me</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-tag">PR & Marketing Consultant</div>
    <h1>I make brands <em>impossible to ignore.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      10+ years. Three continents. One mission: <strong>get you seen, heard, and respected</strong> by the right people. I'm Zuhura — senior PR strategist, media relations expert, and the person your brand calls when you're tired of being the best-kept secret in your industry.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Let's Talk ↗</a>
      <a href="#wins" class="btn btn-outline">See My Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-graphic"></div>
    <div class="hero-stat-grid">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">10+</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Years Experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">30+</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Media Placements</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">3</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Continents Served</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">∞</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">Stories to Tell</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-label">The Human Behind the Headlines</div>
    <h2>Strategic. Sharp. <em>Occasionally Funny.</em></h2>
    <div class="about-grid fade-in">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>I've been doing this long enough to know that <strong>the best PR isn't about spinning stories</strong> — it's about finding the genuine, compelling truth inside your brand and putting it in front of exactly the right people, in exactly the right way.</p>
        <p>I've worked with Silicon Valley entrepreneurs, US law firm networks, wellness coaches, tech founders, authors, and global remote teams. I've pitched journalists at 6am, managed crisis comms at midnight, and celebrated a <em>BBC feature</em> like it was a national holiday (because honestly, it was).</p>
        <p>What I bring to the table isn't just media contacts and a content calendar. It's <strong>strategic thinking, executive-level partnership, and a genuine commitment to making you look spectacular</strong> — without the agency markup, the account manager runaround, or the monthly report nobody reads.</p>
        <p>I work remotely, I work smart, and I deliver. That's the whole pitch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-facts">
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">🌍</div>
          <div class="fact-body">
            <div class="fact-title">Based in Nairobi, Kenya</div>
            <div class="fact-desc">Working with US, UK, and international clients across time zones. Flexibility is kind of my thing.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">🎓</div>
          <div class="fact-body">
            <div class="fact-title">BA Communication & Media — Maseno University</div>
            <div class="fact-desc">Followed by 10+ years of getting things done in the real world, which honestly taught me more.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">⚡</div>
          <div class="fact-body">
            <div class="fact-title">Full-Stack PR & Marketing</div>
            <div class="fact-desc">Strategy, media pitching, content, social, events, executive comms — yes, all of it. No, I don't sleep.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">🤝</div>
          <div class="fact-body">
            <div class="fact-title">Executive Business Partner Experience</div>
            <div class="fact-desc">I've operated as strategic right-hand to CEOs — building SOPs, automating workflows, aligning teams. I think like a founder.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">💬</div>
          <div class="fact-body">
            <div class="fact-title">Fluent in English & Swahili</div>
            <div class="fact-desc">Communicating across cultures is literally in the job description. And I happen to enjoy it.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
